through service.

23:30.326 --> 23:32.317
( scoffs )

23:33.580 --> 23:35.662
Now...

23:37.208 --> 23:40.120
You're not the problem.

23:40.295 --> 23:42.581
We lost people.

23:42.755 --> 23:44.791
That was the problem.

23:44.966 --> 23:46.172
Hanson cracked.

23:46.342 --> 23:48.128
