that got people killed.

23:50.346 --> 23:52.177
Dawn took care of things.

23:53.516 --> 23:55.677
She took care of him.

23:57.854 --> 23:59.970
She saw us past it.

24:00.148 --> 24:01.854
Kept us together.

24:03.151 --> 24:05.016
Kept us alive.

24:07.322 --> 24:09.313
You call this living?

24:09.490 --> 24:11.071
( chuckles )

24:12.327 --> 24:14.158
